OL,6,FA five-bedroom mansion once owned by a
OL,7,Fscammer who defrauded Royal Mail of
OL,8,F#70 million has gone up for sale after
OL,9,Fbeing seized.
OL,11,FComplete with a detached pool house,
OL,12,Fthe near-#3 million property is the
OL,13,Fformer home of Narinder Sandhu, 62,
OL,14,Fwho used the proceeds of an elaborate
OL,15,Fpostage scam to buy it along with a
OL,16,FBentley and a Rolls-Royce.
