OL,4,CRoyal Mail fraudster goes up for sale
OL,6,FMillions of pounds were pocketed in
OL,7,Fthe decade-long fraud, which involved
OL,8,Fthe under-declaration of mail that was
OL,9,Fposted through a network of logistics
OL,10,Fcompanies in Buckinghamshire and
OL,11,FBerkshire from 2005.
OL,13,FSandhu, owner of Packpost
OL,14,FInternational Ltd and the "architect"
OL,15,Fof the fraud, pleaded guilty to the
OL,16,Foffence.
