OL,3,CMultimillion-pound former home of
OL,4,CRoyal Mail fraudster goes up for sale
OL,6,FHis declared taxable income was about
OL,7,F#1 million per year towards the end of
OL,8,Fthe period the fraud was running, a
OL,9,Ftrial at Southwark Crown Court was
OL,10,Ftold last year.
OL,12,FHis brother, Parmjeet Sandhu, 56, from
OL,13,FSlough, pleaded guilty to a charge of
OL,14,Fobtaining services dishonestly.
OL,16,FProsecutor Ellis Sareen said Narinder
OL,17,FSandhu lived with his family at Hadley
OL,18,FGrange, a "multimillion-pound mansion".
