OL,7,Fwealthy, but still made "a lot of
OL,8,Fmoney", Mr Sareen added.
OL,10,F"In this case, we will be talking
OL,11,Fabout literal tonnes of mail `
OL,12,Fthousands of items.
OL,14,F"This has cost Royal Mail about #70
OL,15,Fmillion or a little more. (The
OL,16,Fdefendants) have not pocketed #70
OL,17,Fmillion, but they have benefited."
