OL,3,CMultimillion-pound former home of
OL,4,CRoyal Mail fraudster goes up for sale
OL,6,FBy 2016, so many companies were being
OL,7,Foperated by the group they were
OL,8,F"starting to forget" where they were
OL,9,Flocated, Mr Sareen said.
OL,11,FThe fraud was discovered only when
OL,12,FRoyal Mail customers said competitors
OL,13,Fwere offering unrealistic rates.
OL,15,FWhen investigators became suspicious
OL,16,Fabout the group's companies, all their
OL,17,Fmail was diverted and checked, at
OL,18,Fwhich point it was found their
OL,19,Fpostings had been "significantly
OL,20,Funderdeclared," the prosecutor said.
